deck: This was a temporary job. Peter never made comics before this time, but did doodle a bit. He had to learn in a hurry. Still, it did teach him to appreciate the craft and he met some very talented people on the job.

deck: Canadian comedic actor, best known for his roles in Arrested Development and Superbad.
description:
Comic Related Roles

Scott Pilgrim

Michael Cera played the titular character of Scott Pilgrim in the Edgar Wright-directed film Scott Pilgrim vs. the World. While the film didn't do well at the box office, it has since gained a cult following, being well loved for its attention to detail and respect to Bryan Lee O'Malley's source material.

Cera also voiced Pilgrim in Scott Pilgrim vs. the Animation, an animated short that serves as a prequel to the film.
name: Michael Cera
